-- ECB's Trichet Sees `Good Consensus' by Europe Leaders on Bank Stress Tests
-- Meera Louis
-- 2010-06-17T15:48:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/ecb-s-trichet-sees-good-consensus-by-europe-leaders-on-bank-stress-tests.html

          
          
             European Central Bank President
Jean-Claude Trichet said European Union leaders reached a “good
consensus” on bank stress tests.  
 The results of the stress tests will be published “at the
latest the second half of July,” Trichet told reporters today
in Brussels after a summit of EU leaders.  
